    {
      "parameters": {
        "content": "# Overview\nWhen schedule or webhook fires, this workflow auto-reprices products:\n\n1. Fetch products from WooCommerce\n2. Get competitor prices by SKU\n3. Generate AI price recommendation\n4. Validate margin and discount rules\n5. Update WooCommerce or log failure\n6. Notify admin and continue batch",
        "height": 344,
        "width": 332,
        "color": 3
      },
      "id": "c01dc3e1-690b-463b-a93a-8b4f1acf0fb0",
      "name": "Note: Overview",
      "type": "n8n-nodes-base.stickyNote",
      "typeVersion": 1,
      "position": [
        -1232,
        80
      ]
    },
    {
      "parameters": {
        "content": "# Node-by-node Purpose\n\n1. Schedule Trigger\nRuns on schedule\n\n2. Competitor Price Webhook\nListens for competitor updates\n\n3. Fetch All Products\nGets up to 100 products\n\n4. Fetch Product by SKU\nGets single product from webhook\n\n5. Merge Product Sources\nCombines both triggers\n\n6. Process Per Product\nHandles one product at a time\n\n7. Fetch Competitor Prices\nCalls competitor API\n\n8. AI Pricing Agent\nRecommends new price\n\n9. Validate Pricing Rules\nChecks margin and discount\n\n10. Price Valid?\nRoutes valid vs invalid\n\n11. Update WooCommerce Price\nUpdates live price\n\n12. Log Failure to Sheets\nSaves failed decisions\n\n13. Notify Gmail: Invalid Price\nEmails admin alert\n\n14. Wait\nPauses between items\n\n15. Google Gemini Chat Model\nPowers the AI agent\n\n16. Simple Memory\nProvides short memory",
        "height": 852,
        "width": 328,
        "color": 2
      },
      "id": "e272d670-d46a-41d1-9cea-3723bd3170b3",
      "name": "Note: Node-by-node",
      "type": "n8n-nodes-base.stickyNote",
      "typeVersion": 1,
      "position": [
        1920,
        0
      ]
    }
